Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.00,0:00:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm a soldier  而那也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.27,0:00:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.54,0:00:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同時站在火線的兩端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.14,0:00:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繞過危險的轉角  追過生與死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.62,0:00:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奔向前挑戰謊言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.55,0:00:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論編織出多少謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.23,0:00:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相還是會照出光明的輪廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.20,0:00:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.77,0:00:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.31,0:00:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當我們的痛苦都拋在腦後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.64,0:00:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.28,0:00:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.91,0:01:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是士兵不是站著就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.35,0:01:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.88,0:01:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佔好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.49,0:01:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它們留給審判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.82,0:01:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.42,0:01:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.06,0:01:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犧牲的時候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.73,0:01:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只能奮起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.13,0:01:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻殼機動隊 S.A.C 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.73,0:02:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是九州電波塔上空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.90,0:02:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5天前在地下鐵工地現場發現的未爆彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.37,0:02:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為有人懷疑可能是大戰時使用的戰術核武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.27,0:02:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以開始發動集體避難計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.67,0:02:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在自衛軍的指揮之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.01,0:02:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長達半徑30公里的範圍內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.21,0:02:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,3500萬的一般市民好像終於全部撤退完畢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.91,0:02:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然有部分人士臆測這次事件\N或許又是難民的恐怖攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.92,0:02:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  在政府沒有發表具體消息的狀況下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.42,0:02:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自衛軍封鎖福岡部分地區的這種情勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.69,0:02:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使得街上呈現出如同下達戒嚴令的模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.70,0:02:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#22  無人街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.81,0:03:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因處理爆炸物上行封閉中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.15,0:03:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戒嚴令嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.15,0:03:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,政府的對策確實有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.09,0:03:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  也不必把行政立法司法三權全部委讓給軍方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.99,0:03:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.36,0:03:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世搭乘的偽裝船確實在出島外海沉沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.20,0:03:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是並沒有確定那上面有鈽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.93,0:03:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至於好像為了幫助偽裝船逃走\N所發動的大停電恐怖攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.87,0:03:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也尚未確定是否真的由難民發動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.71,0:03:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,國民對難民的怒氣鞭策政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.55,0:03:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,政府則拿來強化排斥難民的基礎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.72,0:03:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有人肯用自己的腦袋想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.75,0:03:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個結果意味著什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.22,0:03:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算這些都是內廳情報操作的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.79,0:04:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經散佈出去的謠言是無法收回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.73,0:04:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.13,0:04:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.40,0:04:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在出島潛入久世的電子腦之後就有點奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.80,0:04:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的報告書裏面不是有寫嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.74,0:04:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在集中精力處理核彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.68,0:04:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,內廳已經用報導管制的名目出面去控制現場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.78,0:04:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去跟總理交涉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.08,0:04:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請示能否下定決心對內廳展開搜索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.49,0:04:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就靠這些間接證據嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.26,0:04:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在本事件中總理不是也在煩惱\N自衛軍進攻出島這個大問題嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.36,0:04:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這種時期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.26,0:04:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面對可能變成國家醜聞的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不認為總理會點頭同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.74,0:04:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果一個弄得不好  慘遭流彈波及的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.81,0:04:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能又是9課喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.11,0:04:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此我已經安排好讓你們可以介入現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.88,0:04:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去那裏挖點東西出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.92,0:04:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校  我問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.42,0:05:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認為事到如今難民為什麼不開口呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.06,0:05:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相已經在現象面前沉默
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世大概是這麼判斷的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.50,0:05:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在還是保持沉默  甚至對難民也隱瞞真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.84,0:05:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在某處尋找再度扭轉局勢的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.67,0:05:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼這麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.84,0:05:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我如果是他也會這麼做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.12,0:05:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感覺上你的心好像不在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.55,0:05:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們幾個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.05,0:05:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確實是被你的才能吸引才會來到這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.16,0:05:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  並沒有依賴到連當你的後盾都辦不到喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.70,0:05:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.27,0:05:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這種說法我並不討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.94,0:05:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.07,0:05:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你按照預定計劃跟帕茲一起\N參加炸彈處理作業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.84,0:05:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齋藤跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.88,0:05:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂  這是幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.25,0:06:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是所有人一起過去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.68,0:06:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有一個想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.32,0:06:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且我想請你代替我去做某件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.76,0:06:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「日本的奇跡」的準備工作呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.03,0:06:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.96,0:06:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像已經完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.56,0:06:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.80,0:06:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,演變成令人遺憾的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.34,0:06:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炸彈的拆除作業完成後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.31,0:06:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們將召開記者會對國民發表事實真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.88,0:06:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來大概會演變到\N准許自衛軍進攻出島吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.48,0:06:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.42,0:06:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正如報告書中提到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.35,0:06:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鈽交到難民手上的可能性極低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.86,0:06:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓事情惡化到這個程度的多半就是內廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.19,0:06:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在希望您協助暫緩進攻出島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.33,0:06:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那份報告書我看過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.34,0:06:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是已經超過時限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.50,0:06:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,政府根據俄國當局給的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.81,0:07:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,認定鈽已經運進出島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.41,0:07:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並以這一點為決策方針
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.28,0:07:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請原諒我插一句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.82,0:07:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不正是內廳的意圖嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.95,0:07:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明沒有人希望這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.69,0:07:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是等在自衛軍進攻前方的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.32,0:07:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是跟難民間的戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.76,0:07:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何  請在內閣會議\N重新討論報告書的內容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.36,0:07:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果能更早一點看到這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.27,0:07:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對我來說  公安9課也是最後一張牌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.44,0:07:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,荒卷課長  暫時先這樣待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.38,0:07:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.10,0:07:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,6班  13班聯絡本部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.30,0:07:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最上層已經部署完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是公安9課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.37,0:08:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總理命令我們過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.41,0:08:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒聽過這件事喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.77,0:08:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.91,0:08:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是在事件現場常有的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.11,0:08:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.35,0:08:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏有總理的簽名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.78,0:08:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要安排這邊的技術人員到第一線就可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.79,0:08:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法  帶他們過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.62,0:08:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.79,0:08:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼  你想幹什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.86,0:08:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我找那個西裝組人員有點事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.03,0:08:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.43,0:08:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托你的福讓我們幾乎要關門大吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.80,0:08:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過有兩三件事無論如何想要請教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.61,0:08:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.55,0:08:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那個嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.32,0:08:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花五天時間分析構造之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.19,0:08:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在終於要進行拆除作業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.23,0:09:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是公安9課的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.70,0:09:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼能交給他們的事情請盡量指派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.77,0:09:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,To 茅葺 With Love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.90,0:09:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真低級的情書
